                    <value>&lt;br /&gt;
Hi&amp;nbsp;{{{Recipient.FirstName}}},&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Please follow all pre-procedure instructions to achieve optimal results for your upcoming visit:&amp;nbsp;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Avoid excessive sun exposure for 3 days prior to treatment. Treatment cannot be done with a sunburn.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Wash your hair/scalp prior&amp;nbsp;your&amp;nbsp;treatment.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Do not apply any hair products or lotions the same day of your appointment.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Do not apply cleansers or lotions the same day of treatment.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Hair routines can be resumed the day after treatment.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;The scalp may appear bloody until the following day, but it can be washed as usual the next morning.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Bring a CLEAN hat or head covering to your appointment to wear after treatment.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Maintain a healthy diet and drink at least 64 ounces of water the day of the treatment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
For best results, discontinue the use of anti-inflammatory agents a&amp;nbsp;minimum of 3 days before and 3 weeks after your treatment.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
These anti-inflammatory agents include:&amp;nbsp;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Asprin&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;NSAIDs (Motrin, ibuprofen, Aleve, Advil, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Essential fatty acids (EPS, DHA)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Vitamin A&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Turmeric&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Garlic&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Ginger&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Cayenne Pepper&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
If you have any questions about this list or anything pertaining to your upcoming procedure, please don&amp;#39;t hesitate to reach out.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
To your wellness,&lt;br aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; /&gt;
